title: Weather Forecast
description: Write a program that takes in the temperature and humidity and outputs the weather forecast based on the following conditions: if the temperature is above 25 and the humidity is above 60, output 'Rainy', if the temperature is above 25 and the humidity is below 60, output 'Sunny', if the temperature is below 25 and the humidity is above 60, output 'Cloudy', if the temperature is below 25 and the humidity is below 60, output 'Windy'.
